Package car.shared.input

Interface Summary
Interface Description
SliderImpl The interface specifying functions required for an implementation for the Slider class.
 

Class Summary
Class Description
Slider Represents a slider control in an HTML form.
SliderImplGeneral The SliderImpl implementation used for most web browsers.
SliderImplMozilla The SliderImpl implementation used for Mozilla Firefox, since it doesn't have a native slider implementation.
SliderImplMozilla.SliderBarExtra An extension of SliderBar that fixes some compatibility issues with Firefox and adds support for ChangeHandlers and ValueChangeHandlers.
